description:
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Are you an experienced Business Development Professional, seeking a new opportunity to join an innovative, not-for-profit social enterprise, with a culture based on people and how we help and support them?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;This position will support our ambitious growth plans and we are looking for commercially astute individuals that can bring fresh and innovative thinking.&lt;/span&gt; You will set and deliver the Business Development pipeline in collaboration with the Executive team and have valuable experience gained in a similar senior management role.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;You will need to be accomplished in the field of business development, including mergers and acquisitions and confident in developing external relationships and networks to ensure Spectrum is fully appraised for future developments. This will require someone with a decisive nature and clear ambition for success.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;The role will strategically support a culture that inspires service excellence, innovation and maximises all opportunities to sell the services that we deliver. Developing and maintaining a culture that allows for service improvement while role modelling Spectrum’s mission, values and behaviours.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;To apply for this position please complete the short application and attach your CV.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
